      "description": "This A80 chassis features the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant, delivering robust torque through its sequential twin-turbocharged system. The Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission remains crisp, paired with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its driver-grade status, the mechanical vitals are sound, featuring a well-maintained cooling system and factory double-wishbone suspension geometry. A highly capable, driver-focused example of Japanese performance engineering.",
